Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protected witness has left the room. Arriving shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:56.27,Sign-Sans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(400,3000)\fsp2\b1\blur0\fs42\pos(368,194)\t(1000,3000,\blur3)}Time of Eve
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:59.37,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how similar they look, they are still different from humans of flesh and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:02.47,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in the case of androids which are used for sexual purposes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:04.15,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Sexaroids are just urban legends!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.15,0:01:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just going to make the declining birth rates even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:15.76,Sign-Serif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(360,190)}Love doesn't lie there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:16.76,Sign-Sans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(730,0)\1c&HFFFFFF&\fs35\pos(296,261)}Ethics Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't this commercial been appearing more and more recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.72,0:01:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Status, Rikuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At 12:03 PM, he left the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears he will be having lunch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one just saying it, but
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you come here really often when you are free, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.35,0:01:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... Skipping classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.59,0:01:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compensatory holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't something a shop assistant should say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Aside from Rikuo-kun, I thought Masaki-kun was a bit of a delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a scholarship student, surprisingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything unnecessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something to hide anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you're looking for someone to talk to, there are other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always carry that with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I use it to shoot various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'll get around to it eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome. I'll bring over your after-meal Evlend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evlend... Evlend...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've stopped feeling uncomfortable about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Not my reading glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chie, give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.67,0:02:17.32,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:18.24,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be no point just sitting around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we just want to know what this café is all about,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no intention of getting close to any of the robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know about anyone other than Akiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about them, to my right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Dori-kei getting sexual with his own android.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No further explanation needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.30,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't staring!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:45.34,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:46.57,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't staring!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.57,0:02:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were staring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:47.49,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't staring!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were staring!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:48.68,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,You two sure get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't heard that one before!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:49.85,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just two boys getting all excited is pretty lonely you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time I catch you staring...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:54.25,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't staring!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're jealous of Koji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:02:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:00.72,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just very interested, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you two join us here?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.87,0:03:09.00,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord2\be1\c&HF0F3FF&\3c&HBAC2ED&\fs34\fnAkbar\b1\move(354,83,354,94,0,4404)}Time of Eve's rule
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.87,0:03:09.00,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord2\be1\c&HF0F3FF&\3c&HBAC2ED&\fs28\fnAkbar\move(354,112,354,122,0,4404)}In this shop,
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.87,0:03:09.00,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord2\be1\fs28\c&HD5D5FF&\3c&HBEBDFD&\fnAkbar\move(355,165,355,171,0,4404)}there is no discrimination
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.87,0:03:09.00,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord2\be1\fs28\c&HD5D5FF&\3c&HBEBDFD&\fnAkbar\move(354,229,354,233,0,4404)}between humans and robots.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.87,0:03:09.00,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord2\be1\fs28\c&HD5D5FF&\fnAkbar\3c&H827FFD&\move(359,328,356,323,0,4404)}Customers, please cooperate.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.87,0:03:09.00,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord2\be1\fs28\fnAkbar\c&HCDCCFF&\3c&H7479DB&\move(359,406,358,392,0,4404)}Obey the rule and have a fun time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be better not to do anything unnecessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it unnecessary, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it would have been more consistent to let things develop independently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four people will simulate more conversation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:28.77,Sign-Sans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(1000,0)\fsp1\c&H6E6C71&\pos(359,269)}- Lovers of Eve -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Koji, I'm Rina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:45.82,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Masaki, this guy here is Rikuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time you stare, I'll smack you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:53.75,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't staring!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subconsciously huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:56.63,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,You two get...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two get along well, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:58.00,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't heard that one before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:03:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you sure come here often.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you two come here together?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is going splendidly, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's the Cinema Tide?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Oh... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The switch is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.02,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:52.77,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see a preview of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if you press that triangle over there..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.97,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a much-discussed model, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capacity's massive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put 500 into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the M-LINK, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, Cine-tide sure is awesome after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... That's about it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I turn this off?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:06:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's far... Your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much we meet, or get close to each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, I understand the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite a drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what do you call it? A scene of carnage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:12.63,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Protected witness has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was deployed as my master's guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Koji is..?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up till now, what have I been doing??
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the emergency repairs were incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To come here, was for Koji's, that is
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your master's protection?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I took my own initiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That... Shouldn't it be looked at by the manufacturer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have anything to do with my legal manufacturer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my maker were to find out about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my master will be at a disadvantageous position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other than that, I would like to be here a little longer too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even going for repairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this store, the one who acts the least natural as a human
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would not be surprised if I were destroyed sooner rather than later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I am autonomously resisting my useless learning functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koji has... Treated someone like me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the state of a human female.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I think when I am here... I am happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the woman in the photograph...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kind, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll be alright,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I think Koji's kindness will not change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the flavour of the coffee changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was angry at first, but
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I came to understand various things, I was happy, if just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Even though the other person isn't a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him what you want to tell him, even if he's a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Do you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, don't you, the feelings you had at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... How did I come to say such things...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're serious about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's been bothering me since just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is not a single picture of you with Rina.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess you couldn't have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be bad if people knew you had a make-believe lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... If this one was a robot too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:50.44,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then all the more so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not my make-believe lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then are you saying this relationship is for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"There is love,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's not what you're trying to say, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to say this:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"For a human, a human partner is the best."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you do understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you have said, Rina and I cannot transcend the relationship between a human and an android.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think there are things we cannot understand about each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you could understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,want to help my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My master is very similar to Rina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, too, I saw a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.19,0:11:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, master...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, you should look for a new partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.76,0:11:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A human one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough. I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So stay with me always.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My master is morbidly dependent on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know what to do about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met Rina, I thought this person was the same as my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way she behaves and touches me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the fleeting expressions she sometimes shows me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know more about Rina, to better understand my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the First Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About all this... Can you keep it quiet from Rina?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The café's rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hurt anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever suits you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you being a useless person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems no one can really attain happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.35,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,415)\i1}We should {\alpha&HFF&}get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:31.52,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,415)\i1}We should get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there are all sorts:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Androids too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about hitting you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean your eyes were accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have taken a good look myself too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.20,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:12:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you awoken?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a junior high student just reaching my puberty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Rina is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:13.89,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's the other way round, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say Rina was?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To come here, was for Koji's, that is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your master's protection?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She never once said her master was Koji.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.45,0:13:39.00,Sign-Sans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fad(500,0)\c&HCDCDCD&\fs20\move(340.5,245,503.5,245,4073,4532)}Master
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't say it.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.50,0:13:39.00,Sign-Sans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fad(500,0)\c&HCDCDCD&\fs20\pos(172.5,245)}Master
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside of this store, they are unrelated?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they both said the other is human.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.46,0:13:40.46,Sign-Sans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HCDCDCD&\fs20\pos(418.5,240)}Human
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.46,0:13:40.46,Sign-Sans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HCDCDCD&\fs20\pos(261.5,225)}Human
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a discrepancy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:42.71,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go! Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They might not have realized... About each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. That's it for the hints.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you please explain this properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partners not knowing what the other is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same for androids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pair of them are mutually interested in each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the wrong reasons, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They also have things they are hiding from each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like normal love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've said something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, don't interfere too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love between androids...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pseudo-love, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:19.83,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,So the woman in the photo the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A love triangle between androids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:24.61,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit hard to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A difficult-to-explain woman, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:28.10,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Androids tangled in blind love...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go into weird deviations!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll tell me about it properly someday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, master.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.27,0:14:48.78,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&}Nao and mum have gone out for {\b1}dinner{\b0}.\NSammy, please take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you put on your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not like it?
